 who?-wrote The Medium is the Message, he must have had this film partially in mind.\n\nGriffith is perfect: he is a mixture of cornpone and Satan.  Patricia Neal is the woman-frequently abandoned and abused--who discovered the man and loves him for what she thought he was. Walter Matthau is the Princeton man who becomes one of the many faceless writers behind the fa\u00e7ade of the county wit-Rhodes: the man admired for his `extempore and natural' humor. \n\n Watch early on in the film for a scene taking place in the local jail.  In one quick and brief flash of expression, Griffith reveals the true face of Lonesome Rhodes the rest of the film tries to mask.  What brilliant acting by Griffith; what brilliant screen writing by Budd Schulberg; what brilliant directing by Kazan.", "reviewRating": {"@type": "Rating", "worstRating": "1", "bestRating": "10", "ratingValue": "10"}}, "duration": "PT2H6M", "trailer": {"@type": "VideoObject", "name": "A Face in the Crowd", "embedUrl": "/video/imdb/vi1630977049", "thumbnail": {"@type": "ImageObject", "contentUrl": "https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BZGE1OGQ5ZjgtYzRjNS00MzE4LWE4MTMtZDA3MGU2YTY5OGQ2XkEyXkFqcGdeQXRoaXJkLXBhcnR5LXZpZGVvLXVwZGF0ZXI@._V1_.jpg"}, "thumbnailUrl": "https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BZGE1OGQ5ZjgtYzRjNS00MzE4LWE4MTMtZDA3MGU2YTY5OGQ2XkEyXkFqcGdeQXRoaXJkLXBhcnR5LXZpZGVvLXVwZGF0ZXI@._V1_.jpg", "description": "Official Trailer", "uploadDate": "2019-06-12T17:01:30Z"}, "cast_and_character": [{"actor": {"@type": "Person", "url": "/name/nm0341431/?ref_=tt_cl_t1", "name": "Andy Griffith"}, "character_and_episodes": [{"url": "/title/tt0050371/characters/nm0341431?ref_=tt_cl_t1", "name": "Larry 'Lonesome' Rhodes"}]}, {"actor": {"@type": "Person", "url": "/name/nm0290047/?ref_=tt_cl_t3", "name": "Anthony Franciosa"}, "character_and_episodes": [{"url": "/title/tt0050371/characters/nm0290047?ref_=tt_cl_t3", "name": "Joey DePalma"}]}, {"actor": {"@type": "Person", "url": "/name/nm0001665/?ref_=tt_cl_t5", "name